      • read_file

        public static void read_file(java.lang.String[] args)
        read_file This function reads from a given input file based on the number of command line arguments. In case a file is passed over the command line, then the application considers it as the input. In case a command line argument is not passed, the program asks the user how the user wants to enter the input file. If the user enters 1, the user is asked to enter the file name. In case the user enters 2, the user can enter the whole file through standard input.
        Parameters:
        args - Command Line Arguments
